title.rendered: Faro Outdoor Lounge Armchair Set – end of line

content.rendered:
This item is due to be discontinued. Price available whilst stocks last.

–

The Faro outdoor lounge set comprises of two comfortable armchairs, with cushion & optional table.

Ideal for mid-commercial use, such as coffee shops, hotels and care homes. Easy to clean and care for – suitable for all weather, indoor and out!

Made with injection moulded rattan effect plastic resin. 5 year warranty. Easy to assemble. Antifungal & Colourfast. Items can be purchased separately, in quantities of 2.
